      "comment": "Stage 5 \u2014 the v1 wiring of file action handlers through Path.Authorize.\nThis test exercises the in-root happy path: file.save then file.read both\ngo through Authorize, both auto-grant (in-root), the round-trip works.\nThe out-of-root prompt/sign/store scenarios are exercised by the C# Stage 5\ntests (PLang.Tests/App/FileSystem/Stage5MessagesEndToEndTests.cs) \u2014 the\nPLang test runner can\u0027t easily set up real OS-out-of-root paths because\nValidatePath prefixes /-rooted paths with the test\u0027s RootDirectory.",
